    .col-md-3
      p.
        Who needs wards to guess where your opponents are? With Hyperopia,
        your days of wasting gold as a support are over and you can instead focus on the
        Agh's that you will definitely finish. How do you know? Hyperopia.
    .col-md-3
      p.
        Why wait for your teammates to make mistakes before you mock them?
        With Hyperopia, you can be sure to have all your one-liners prepared as
        they get they get triple-killed because you didn't call missing.
    .col-md-3
      p.
        Ever call "GG" in the first 5 minutes of gameplay? With Hyperopia,
        you'll know your excellent predictions will be right every time.
    .col-md-3
      p Know ahead of time to go full retard.
  hr
  .row
    .col-md-12.text-center
      h3 NSASight reveals personal player details
      p Charge up your flames and hurt them where it hurts
  .row.text-center
    .col-md-3
      p.lead Locations
      span.fa.fa-map-marker.fa-5x
      p.text(style="margin-top:1em;") Yep. Explains that.
    .col-md-3
      p.lead Food
      span.fa.fa-cutlery.fa-5x
      p.text(style="margin-top:1em;") Know their favorite snacks.
    .col-md-3
      p.lead IQ
      span.fa.fa-cogs.fa-5x
      p.text Also explains that.
    .col-md-3
      p.lead(style='margin-top:25%;') and more!

  hr
  .row
    .col-md-12
      h3.text-center YASP++ Benefits
      .col-md-8
        h3 YASP Basic
        .row
          .col-md-4
            p #[i.fa.fa-plus] Player Profile
            p #[i.fa.fa-plus] Public Statistics
